The '''Pomegranate''' is a [[Fruits|fruit]] grown by planting a [[Pomegranate Sapling]], waiting 28 days for it to grow into a [[Pomegranate Tree]], and harvesting the tree during the [[Fall]].

A Pomegranate may be purchased at the [[Traveling Cart]] for {{tprice|140}} or found in [[The Cave|The Farm Cave]], if the fruit bat option is chosen.

==Gifting==
{{GiftsByItem
|like=Robin,Demetrius,Maru,Sebastian,Linus,Pierre,Caroline,Abigail,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Penny,Pam,Emily,Haley,Jas,Vincent,Jodi,Kent,Sam,Leah,Shane,Marnie,Gus,Dwarf,Wizard,Harvey,Sandy,Willy,Krobus,Leo
