==Bundles==
Pomegranate is used in the {{Bundle|enchanter||y}}, and is an option for the {{Bundle|Artisan||y}}.

==Recipes==
Pomegranate is not used in any recipes.

==Tailoring==
Pomegranate can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring#Pants|Relaxed Fit Pants]].  [[File:Relaxed Fit Pants.png|36px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as a purple dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
Pomegranate is not used in any [[quests]].

==History==
{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].}}

